metadata.name: Meltdown Maltese
metadata.description: VeeFiends was created in honor of Gary Vaynerchuk. The creator of VeeFriends. VeeFiends are 268 hand-drawn, parody artworks stored on the Ethereum blockchain. Holders will gain access to exclusive giveaways, mini-games, global leaderboards and be a part of a fun, lighthearted community. And the biggest benefit of all, VeeFiends holders will participate in a lottery to win up to 15 grand prizes - Return flight, hotel accommodation and entry to VeeCon 2022 and beyond!
